(60158, 128435, 0, 1, '南海路深夜對談(Demo)', '這是C++成軍後第一首歌,\r\n獻給我們的母校, 還有那堆有的沒的回憶.\r\nEnjoy it !!', '2013-01-31 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, 'We''ve come to nowhere\r\nHesitating and so we stroll\r\nAlong the path leading to fogs and  shadows\r\nAnd so we walk and crawl with fear\r\n \r\nThe sky seems too gray \r\nColorless, no hope\r\nNostalgia occupies my mind\r\nI wonder if it''s better we forget\r\n \r\nWe were to perspire\r\nBut we''ve never had a clue\r\nAbout here and everything that''s so unclear\r\nAnd about all these things we bear in mind\r\n \r\n灰色的天空和人啊\r\n是不是都不想要看見\r\n長大後未來在哪裡\r\n伸出手究竟能不能抓住未來\r\n \r\nThe sky seems too grey \r\nColorless, no hope\r\nNostalgia occupies my mind\r\nI wonder if it''s better we forget\r\n', '', 400, '', 'How to Program C++', '瑪莉', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1, '2013-01-31 18:44:37', '2013-10-07 17:23:51', '2013-05-10 18:37:40'),
(60159, 164993, 0, 1, 'We are (demo)', '繁忙的生活  維持著物質評的同時\r\n是否快要忘記當時夢想是甚麼....?', '2013-01-31 00:00:00', 2013, 0, 1, 4, 'We are \r\n\r\n抬起頭仰望著天空\r\n腳下還躊躇著什麼\r\n若還有夢\r\n不怕一切困難阻擋著我\r\n\r\n很清楚永恆的背後\r\n都有不放棄的推手\r\n我還是我\r\n要讓你看見屬於夢的自由\r\n\r\n雖然別人都笑著說 別作夢\r\n實際點 人生不會錯\r\n如果連伸手觸及的 都沒把握\r\n青春只會剩下寂寞\r\n\r\n越遠的路 越高的夢\r\n越要能到達 裝上勇敢翅膀展翅去飛翔\r\n就算寄託 越來越重\r\n邁開步伐 這就是我要走的路不回頭\r\n', '', 211, '', '小七/李毛/米奇', '莎莎', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-01-31 18:52:49', '2015-03-12 13:59:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(60160, 171614, 0, 1, '聞你香 URAROMA', '2008年夏秋, 為了練吉他寫的歌, 此中英版為2013年1月31日春吶報名截止日當天在烏來的家, 以吉他自彈自唱, 多軌錄音機錄製', '2012-12-21 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 6, 'Your aroma makes me high\r\nI wanna put it in a bag and seal it\r\nTake it with me when I go to bed\r\nTravel with me on the rickshaw or RV\r\nWondering and getting lost from the holly river of Varanasi,\r\nto the big open dusty Burning Man playa\r\nYour aroma is the efficacious magic spell\r\nMy heart swells whenever I smell you\r\nYour kisses are sweeter than maple syrup, coconut milk and honey\r\nThat milts in me, releasing nectar of love\r\nI wanna be wherever you are, so that I can smell you\r\n\r\n聞你香令我亢奮\r\n我想把你的味道,裝進袋子裡封好,陪我上床睡覺\r\n跟我一起去旅行,搭三輪或露營車\r\n迷走或閒晃,在 varanasi 神聖的恒河岸邊\r\n與火人節浩瀚沙漠之間\r\n\r\n伱的味道是靈驗的魔法咒語\r\n只要一聞到你,我心就澎漲\r\n伱的吻比楓糖椰奶加蜂蜜還甜\r\n在我體內融化,釋放愛的瓊漿玉液\r\n\r\n不管你去哪我都要跟著,這樣才能聞你味道', '', 175, '', '吳音霓 Winnie', '吳音霓 Winnie', '吳音霓 Winnie', 'OMNIVOYAGE.ORG', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-01-31 18:58:50', '2015-03-12 13:59:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(60161, 171614, 0, 1, '念頭 SOULUTION', '2008年夏秋, 為了練吉他寫的歌, 有中英兩版, 此中文版為2013年1月31日春吶報名截止日當天在烏來的家, 以及他自彈自唱, 多軌錄音機錄製', '2012-12-22 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 6, '念頭\r\n\r\n有人在盪鞦韆,來回擺盪\r\n有人在蹺蹺板上,反覆踱步\r\n閉上眼,看見,什麼不見,什麼浮現\r\n何不接受我們無法控制的事\r\n\r\n心懸疑慮,別亂動,靜凝神細聽\r\n洞察靈光乍現,知所當為\r\n跟虛無的人造罪惡感說再見,歸還借來的原罪\r\n\r\n內有源頭活水來灌溉,自我成長波及週遭\r\n睜開靈性之眼,看見天堂\r\n收集智慧的種子,隨緣禪定萌芽,灑一把故鄉的泥土,強化磁場\r\nWakan tanka,生命的奧秘,催化,分解,思考就是耕耘遠景\r\n\r\n從宇宙中心提氣,在根源與結尾交會的地方深呼吸\r\n思緒沸騰,意識流整合\r\n神奇玄秘的介入力量,引發微妙革命,帶來深刻體悟\r\n\r\nSoulution\r\n\r\nSomeone is swinging to and fro\r\nSomeone is walking on a titer tater back and forth\r\nSeeing with our eyes shut, what’s fading? What’s emerging?\r\nWhy not accept things beyond our control\r\nWhen in doubt do nothing, quite your mind and listen carefully\r\nObserving till the moment of knowing what is for sure the right things to do\r\nsay good bye to feeling of artificial guiltiness\r\nreturn the borrowed original sin\r\n\r\nThere is a fountain flows in me growing from one self to the surroundings\r\nHeaven exists when our spiritual eyes open\r\nGather seeds of wisdom, sprouting with affinity in zen,\r\nSprinkle a handful of home town dirt to enhance the vibration\r\n\r\nWakan Tanka~ great mystery of life\r\nCatalyzing, decomposing, thinking is to plant vision\r\nDrawing deep breath from cosmic center, where all roots begin and ends meet\r\n\r\nSteaming thoughts bubble, streams of consciousness integrate\r\nMystical intervention trigger subtle revolution, leads to profound realization\r\n', '', 199, '', '吳音霓 Winnie', '吳音霓 Winnie', '吳音霓 Winnie', 'OMNIVOYAGE.ORG', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-01-31 19:00:30', '2015-03-12 13:59:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
