(60164, 171614, 0, 1, '末日狂歡節 DOOMSDAY CARNIVAL', '2008年夏秋, 為了練吉他寫的歌, 有中英兩版, 此自彈自唱中文版為2012年11月於加州自家露營車上, 以電子琴伴奏, 多軌錄音機錄製', '2012-12-21 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 6, '末日狂歡節\r\n\r\n正在從迷宮和老鼠賽跑出來的路上,沿途每道門後面都是漩渦\r\n\r\n每扇窗開啟另一個世界,挑逗慵懶唇舌,搖擺瘋狂骨頭\r\n\r\n打開全身脈輪,順勢而上,言行如一, 也愛跳舞\r\n\r\n吟唱,斷卻幻像枷鎖,轉個彎,出現契機\r\n\r\n和我一起搭乘雲霄飛車,一飛衝天 擁抱星體\r\n\r\n彎腰親吻草地閃亮露珠,循因果報業,萬般自由無礙\r\n\r\n沈重現實更需要,華麗美夢來陪襯\r\n\r\n時機已到,呼喚各路朋友們,現在就集合\r\n\r\n和波西米亞人八卦,跟靈媒聊天,活出真相,見機行事,廣結善緣\r\n\r\n萬事皆虛空,只有學習精神漫無止境,繼續夢下去,漂浮娑影雲端智慧\r\n\r\n清醒地思慮考量,究竟自己每天為什麼起床,一起來伴隨彩虹,一路探險到世界末日\r\n\r\n迎接全新開始\r\n\r\nDoomsday Carnival\r\n\r\nHere We are on the way out of this rat race from cosmic maze\r\nIt’s a vortex behind every door alone the way, and every window opens to another world\r\nTease our lazy tongues, shake our crazy bones, opening all chakras let it flow\r\nWalk the talk, and dance dance dance\r\nChant on to dispel the illusion, and the chances come around the corner\r\n\r\nGetting on this roller coaster ride with me, shooting up high to huddle heavenly bodies\r\nBending down to kiss sparkling dewy grass-rooted ground, it’s all so free under karma tree\r\nGhetto reality needs to match with fancy dreams\r\nIt''s time to call for all circles of friends, get together now\r\n\r\nGossiping Bohemians, chitchatting spirit mediums\r\nLiving truth, improvising, and making good connections\r\nNothing is real, but part of a wholesome lesson to be shared\r\nDream on floating and seeing random wisdom\r\nSoberly wondering and pondering, why on the earth do we wake up everyday\r\n\r\nLet’s follow the rainbows together\r\nAdventure till the end of the world to welcome our new beginning\r\n\r\nMusic:Winnie / Lyrics: Winnie', '', 167, '', '吳音霓 Winnie', '吳音霓 Winnie', '吳音霓 Winnie', 'OMNIVOYAGE.ORG', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-01-31 19:19:40', '2015-03-12 13:59:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
